name: InitializeVoterRegistrationRanges
rule:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `VoterRegistrationRanges` (
  `county_code` char(3) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `voter_id` bigint(18) unsigned NOT NULL,
  `max_election_date` date NOT NULL,
  `min_election_date` date NOT NULL,
  `election_count` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`county_code`,`voter_id`,`max_election_date`,`min_election_date`,`election_count`),
  KEY `county_code` (`county_code`),
  KEY `voter_id` (`voter_id`),
  KEY `max_election_date` (`max_election_date`),
  KEY `min_election_date` (`min_election_date`),
  KEY `election_count` (`election_count`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci
